TITLE:Support BAX - Donations and Community
DESC:Support the development of BAX through donations and community contributions.
IMG:https://placehold.co/1200x400/0f172a/ffffff?text=Support+BAX

H1:Support BAX

H2:Why Support BAX?
P:BAX is an open-source project built with ❤️ by Axcora Tech. Your support helps us maintain, improve, and add new features to BAX.
P:Every contribution, no matter how small, makes a difference!

HR:

H2:Donation Options

H3:GitHub Sponsors
P:Become a sponsor on GitHub and help us keep BAX free and open-source.
P:<a href="https://github.com/sponsors/mesinkasir" class="btn btn-dark">Support on Github</a>
CODE:https://github.com/sponsors/mesinkasir
P:GitHub Sponsors offers monthly or one-time donations.

H3:PayPal
P:Send a one-time donation via PayPal.
P:<a href="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_s-xclick&hosted_button_id=JVZVXBC4N9DAN" class="btn btn-primary">Support on Paypal</a>
CODE:https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_s-xclick&hosted_button_id=JVZVXBC4N9DAN
P:PayPal accepts credit cards, debit cards, and bank transfers.

H3:Buy Me a Coffee
P:Buy us a coffee on Gumroad.
CODE:https://creativitaz.gumroad.com/coffee
P:<a href="https://creativitaz.gumroad.com/coffee" class="btn btn-warning">Buy Me a Coffee</a>
P:Support us with a small contribution and keep us motivated!

HR:

H2:Community

H3:GitHub
P:Report issues, contribute code, or request features:
CODE:https://github.com/mesinkasir/bax

H3:Website
P:Visit our official website for more information:
CODE:https://bax.axcora.com

H3:Documentation
P:Read the complete documentation:
CODE:https://bax.axcora.com/pages/documentation.html

HR:

H2:Contributing
P:We welcome contributions from everyone! Here's how you can help:

H3:Code Contributions
OL:
LI:Fork the repository
LI:Create a feature branch
LI:Make your changes
LI:Submit a pull request
/OL:

H3:Report Issues
P:Found a bug? Report it on GitHub Issues:
CODE:https://github.com/mesinkasir/bax/issues

H3:Spread the Word
P:Share BAX with your friends and colleagues. Star us on GitHub!

HR:

H2:Acknowledgments
P:BAX is built with ❤️ by:

UL:
LI:Axcora Tech - Development and Maintenance
LI:Bootstrap - CSS Framework
LI:Open Source Community - Inspiration and Support
/UL:

HR:

H2:Thank You!
P:Thank you for supporting BAX! Your contributions help us keep the project alive and growing.

BLOCKQUOTE:"Open source is not just about code. It's about community, collaboration, and making the web better for everyone."

